net.minecraftforge.event.entity.living.MobEffectEvent.Added
Enclosing class:
MobEffectEvent
public static class MobEffectEvent.Added extends MobEffectEvent
This event is fired when a new MobEffectInstance is added to an entity. This event is also fired if an entity already has the effect but with a different duration or amplifier. This event is not Cancelable. This event does not have a result.
